{"uuid": "12959076-dd87-4994-bd4f-9f8714edc79b", "id": 23066, "date": "2020-12-09T05:00:02", "date_gmt": "2020-12-09T13:00:02", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=23066"}, "modified": "2020-12-09T05:21:04", "modified_gmt": "2020-12-09T13:21:04", "slug": "cover-me-lorenzo-bertocchini-and-elizabeth-lee-be-true", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/12/09/cover-me-lorenzo-bertocchini-and-elizabeth-lee-be-true/", "title": {"rendered": "Cover Me, Lorenzo Bertocchini and Elizabeth Lee: Be True"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Some songs completely transform when you sing them with someone else.</p>\n<p>Just as &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/02/06/roll-of-the-dice-brilliant-disguise/\">Brilliant Disguise</a>&#8221; morphs from a song about betrayal and estrangement when sung alone into a song of acceptance and commitment when performed as a duet, so does &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/12/02/roll-of-the-dice-be-true/\">Be True</a>&#8221; blossom from a &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/05/28/roll-of-the-dice-two-hearts/\">Two Hearts</a>&#8220;-style pep talk into a pledge of intimacy and devotion.</p>\n<p>Allow Lorenzo Bertocchini and Elizabeth Lee to demonstrate with their breathtakingly tender and beautiful cover of &#8220;Be True&#8221; from the 2010 Italian tribute album, <em>For You 2.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Be True - LORENZO BERTOCCHINI &amp; ELIZABETH LEE\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k-XN1YgqvRA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>Bertocchini is superb on his acoustic guitar and harmonica, and Gabriele Zolli&#8217;s violin is just lovely&#8211;but what truly elevates this cover are the world-weary vocals from Lorenzo and Elizabeth. We get the clear sense that these two characters aren&#8217;t young, na\u00efve lovers. They&#8217;ve been around a time or two, which makes their pledges all the more meaningful and a happy ending much more satisfying.</p>\n<p>Tribute albums can be hit or miss, but this one&#8217;s a bullseye.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Lorenzo Bertocchini and Elizabeth Lee transform &#8220;Be True&#8221; with their beautiful, world-weary, acoustic cover.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 23478, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [4], "tags": [236, 2989, 2988], "class_list": ["post-23066", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-cover-me", "tag-be-true", "tag-elizabeth-lee", "tag-lorenzo-bertocchini"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/betruelorenzo.jpg?fit=500%2C500&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-6